data.description: Great curb appeal. Both living areas have decorator paints and are large and open with lots of light. Kitchen is partially open to den area and is large enough for breakfast table. Built-ins in one bedroom makes great office setting. Backyard is big with nice brick patio under the shade tree. Door in back of garage leads to nice workshop and big storage room. You're going to love it!
